    "Livelox User Agreement" : {
      "comment" : "A link to Livelox's user agreement.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "Location data" : {
      "comment" : "Description of the location data that LoxBridge collects.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "LoxBridge" : {
      "comment" : "The name of the app.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "LoxBridge contains no advertising SDKs, no analytics trackers, and no crash reporting services that transmit your data to third parties." : {
      "comment" : "Text displayed in a privacy row that explains that LoxBridge does not use any advertising SDKs, analytics trackers, or crash reporting services.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "LoxBridge is designed to keep you in control of your personal data. Here's exactly what the app does with it." : {
      "comment" : "A privacy notice that describes how LoxBridge uses user data.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "LoxBridge itself has no accounts and stores no personal information on any server. All settings and route history are stored locally on your device." : {
      "comment" : "Text displayed in a privacy notice that informs users that LoxBridge does not store any user data on a server.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "LoxBridge only reads health data in direct response to a completed workout notification. It does not run persistent background processes that sample your location or health." : {
      "comment" : "Privacy row for the \"No background data collection\" section.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "LoxBridge reads your activity GPS routes from Apple Health and sends them to Livelox — only when you choose. Your data never goes anywhere else, is never sold, and is never used for advertising." : {
      "comment" : "OnboardingView - privacy statement",
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "cs" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "LoxBridge čte GPS trasy vašich aktivit z Apple Health a odesílá je do Livelox — pouze když to zvolíte. Vaše data nikam jinam nejdou, nikdy se neprodávají a nikdy se nepoužívají pro reklamu."
          }
        },
        "da" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "LoxBridge læser dine aktivitets-GPS-ruter fra Apple Helbred og sender dem til Livelox — kun når du vælger det. Dine data havner aldrig et andet sted, sælges aldrig og bruges aldrig til reklame."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "LoxBridge liest deine Aktivitäts-GPS-Routen aus Apple Gesundheit und sendet sie an Livelox — nur wenn du es wählst. Deine Daten gehen nirgendwo sonst hin, werden nie verkauft und nie für Werbung verwendet."
          }
        },
        "et" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "LoxBridge loeb sinu tegevuse GPS-radasid Apple Tervisest ja saadab need Liveloxisse — ainult siis, kui sa seda valid. Sinu andmed ei lähe kuhugi mujale, neid ei müüda kunagi ega kasutata kunagi reklaamiks."
          }
        },
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "LoxBridge lukee aktiviteetti-GPS-reittisi Apple Terveydestä ja lähettää ne Liveloxiin — vain kun valitset niin. Tietosi eivät mene minnekään muualle, niitä ei koskaan myydä eikä käytetä mainontaan."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "LoxBridge lit vos itinéraires GPS d'activité depuis Apple Santé et les envoie à Livelox — uniquement quand vous le choisissez. Vos données ne vont nulle part ailleurs, ne sont jamais vendues et ne sont jamais utilisées pour la publicité."
          }
        },
        "nb" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "LoxBridge leser aktivitets-GPS-rutene dine fra Apple Helse og sender dem til Livelox — bare når du velger det. Dataene dine havner aldri noe annet sted, selges aldri og brukes aldri til reklame."
          }
        },
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "LoxBridge läser dina aktivitets-GPS-spår från Apple Hälsa och skickar dem till Livelox — bara när du väljer det. Dina data hamnar aldrig någon annanstans, säljs aldrig och används aldrig för reklam."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "LoxBridge reads your Apple Watch and iPhone activity routes through the Apple Health app to generate GPX files. Tap below to grant access." : {
      "comment" : "OnboardingView - HealthKit step description",
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "cs" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "LoxBridge čte trasy aktivit z Apple Watch a iPhonu prostřednictvím aplikace Apple Health pro generování GPX souborů. Klepnutím níže udělte přístup."
          }
        },
        "da" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "LoxBridge læser dine Apple Watch og iPhone aktivitetsruter via Apple Helbred-appen for at generere GPX-filer. Tryk nedenfor for at give adgang."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "LoxBridge liest deine Apple Watch- und iPhone-Aktivitätsrouten über die Apple Health App, um GPX-Dateien zu erstellen. Tippe unten, um Zugriff zu gewähren."
          }
        },
        "et" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "LoxBridge loeb sinu Apple Watchi ja iPhone tegevusradasid Apple Tervise rakenduse kaudu GPX-failide loomiseks. Juurdepääsu andmiseks puuduta allpool."
          }
        },
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "LoxBridge lukee aktiviteettireittisi Apple Watchilta ja iPhonelta Apple Terveys -sovelluksen kautta GPX-tiedostojen luomiseksi. Napauta alla myöntääksesi käyttöoikeuden."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "LoxBridge lit vos itinéraires d'activité depuis l'Apple Watch et l'iPhone via l'application Apple Santé pour générer des fichiers GPX. Appuyez ci-dessous pour accorder l'accès."
          }
        },
        "nb" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "LoxBridge leser aktivitetsrutene dine fra Apple Watch og iPhone via Apple Helse-appen for å generere GPX-filer. Trykk nedenfor for å gi tilgang."
          }
        },
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "LoxBridge läser dina aktivitetsrutter från Apple Watch och iPhone via Apple Hälsa för att skapa GPX-filer. Tryck nedan för att ge åtkomst."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "LoxBridge reads your workouts and GPS routes from the Apple Health app. This data stays on your device and is never shared with anyone other than Livelox, and only when you initiate an upload." : {
      "comment" : "Explanation of how health and workout data is collected by LoxBridge.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "LoxBridge will run in the background. After each outdoor activity you'll receive a notification to upload the route." : {
